headline: Why This Analyst Says It's Time To 'Accumulate' Shares As This Top Nuclear Stock Falls Despite Surprise 20% Profit Gain

headline: Constellation Offers Maryland a Menu of New Generation Options to Meet Rising Demand, Including 5,800 Megawatts of New Power Generation and Battery Storage
summary: BALTIMORE, November 04, 2025--Constellation announced a long-range proposal to invest in up to 5,800 megawatts of power generation and battery storage projects in Maryland.
